additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Water, Sorbitol, Propylene Glycol, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Poloxamer 407, Benzoic Acid, Eucalyptol, Sodium Benzoate, Thymol, Flavor, Sodium Saccharin, Methyl Salicylate, Menthol, Sucralose, CI 47005, CI 42053

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value:
Caution: Do not use if you are allergic to any of the ingredients
  • Keep out of reach of children
  • If an excessive amount is accidentally swallowed or in the event of an adverse reaction, stop use and seek medical attention immediately.
